Package: opennsl-modules
Architecture: amd64
Section: kernel
Depends: linux-image-7.0.0-1002-sonic | linux-image-sonic
Description: kernel modules for Broadcom SAI (SONiC)
 This package provides the kernel modules for Broadcom switch ASICs
 used in the SONiC (Software for Open Networking in the Cloud) platform.
 .
 Includes legacy BDE/KNET modules and next-generation SDKLT modules
 (ngbde, ngknet, ngknetcb) for Broadcom device enumeration and kernel
 networking.
